<div style='padding-bottom:10px;color:#711e23;font-size:25px;' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h1 custom-color-heading blockquote modern-quote  avia-builder-el-8  el_after_av_slideshow  el_before_av_textblock   av-thin-font av-inherit-size '><h1 class='av-special-heading-tag '  itemprop="headline"  ><strong>Superior 401(k) Administration and Actuarial Services</strong></h1><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' style='border-color:#711e23'></div></div></div>
<section class="av_textblock_section "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop="text" ><p>Metro Benefits, Inc. is an independent, full service consulting firm providing a wide array of 401(k) administration and actuarial services for qualified employee retirement benefit plans. Under the management of our professionally credentialed founding principals, we design, implement and administer benefit plans for clients ranging from small businesses to large corporations.</p>
</div></section>
<section class="av_textblock_section "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop="text" ><p>When it comes to employee <strong>retirement benefit plans</strong>, <strong>complying with governmental regulations and guidelines</strong> is extremely important, but also very confusing. At Metro Benefits, we strive to simplify the complex design, implementation and compliance of retirement benefit plans by expertly translating stacks of technical jargon into information that is easy to follow and easy to understand.</p>
</div></section></div>
